Hello everyone, I'm using the js building examples repo and trying to load the mui library in. It builds and deploys fine but I'm getting the following error:
```Error when server rendering @projects/hello-world-project/hello-world-app/components/partials/Item.jsx
SyntaxError: Unexpected token 'export'```
The Item.jsx file looks like this:
```import * as React from 'react';
import Button from '@mui/material/Button';

export default function Item() {
  return &lt;Button variant="contained"&gt;Hello world&lt;/Button&gt;;
}```
